    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="about-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <h1>Thirsting for Knowledge...</h1>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h3>I'm new to the world of development but hungry to learn. After graduating from <strong>Indiana University</strong> in 2011, I held a series of jobs that didn't challenge me: Barista, Bartender, Copy Writer...</h3>
            <h3><strong>I needed to be challeneged.</strong> I needed to learn. I needed something that would stimulate me. I turned to development as an outlet for that hunger and in mid 2016 I dove in head first, signing up for The Iron Yard coding bootcamp in Indianapolis.</h3>
            <h3>Since then I have poured myself into learning as much as I could about development. I started with <strong>Ruby on Rails</strong> and <strong>HTML/CSS</strong>; <strong>JavaScript</strong> came next and I've been striving to learn more.</h3>
            <h3>I'm thrilled to have finally found a career in which I can continue to grow, learn, and challenge myself, to always expand and better myself <strong>and</strong> the impact my work can have on others.</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <%= image_tag "timeline.png", class: "img-responsive"%>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

